warning.title: Before playing NomaiVR, some information:
warning.body:
- Click the NomaiVR readme button in the Mod Manager for information about troubleshooting, requirements, performance, how to uninstall, etc.

- Some VR controllers will have missing icons. Message us if you want to help us add icons for these devices.

- If you have the game on Steam:
--- Right-click Outer Wilds on your Steam library
--- Select 'Properties...'
--- Disable 'Use Desktop Game Theatre.'

releases.name: Quantum Space Buddies
releases.description: Outer Wilds online multiplayer mod, using modified UNET and OWML.
releases.author: misternebula

warning.title: Follow these steps before playing multiplayer :
warning.body:
- Disable *all* other mods. (Can heavily affect performance)
- Make sure you are not running any other network-intensive applications.
- Make sure you have forwarded/opened the correct ports. (See the GitHub readme.)
